msgid ""
"Located at Rue de Neupré 108 in the scenic Osivies area, the <b>Ferme Saint-"
"Jean</b> collection offers four unique apartment options (Units 26–29) that "
"combine modern interior design with the charm of a historic estate. These "
"units are ideal for professionals or small families seeking a quiet, stylish "
"retreat without sacrificing accessibility."
